<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Texas College will offer at least 3 credits to students who earn a score of 3 or higher on the AP exam.  The course(s) credited and the number of credits offered depend on the academic major, AP subject area, and departmental recommendation. Students must be admitted to degree status and currently enrolled to be eligible for AP credit.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.texascollegeonline.net/catalog.asp" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

